long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
NUSO Connect AC SIP is an extension required to use the “NUSO Connect Business” and “Mida Attendant Console Pro.”

By installing the extension NUSO Connect AC SIP, operators using “NUSO Connect Business” and “Mida Attendant Console Pro” will be able to perform all the actions expected by the software (i.e. place and receive calls, transfer calls, place calls in a queue).

IMPORTANT NOTICES AND DISCLAIMERS - PLEASE READ
